com.dua3.meja.model

Interface Workbook

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<Sheet>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GenericWorkbook, PoiWorkbook, PoiWorkbook.PoiHssfWorkbook, PoiWorkbook.PoiXssfWorkbook

    public interface Workbook
extends java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<Sheet>
    Workbook class.

    A workbook consists of different sheets which can be accessed by number or name. Use one of the concrete implementations of WorkbookFactory to read a workbook from disk. Workbooks can be displayed in Swing applications using the WorkbookView class.
